Hi!

You can find below an example to reproduce the problem on https://echarts.apache.org/examples/en/editor.html

- Once loaded, you'll have 6 groups of 4 bars each.
- Start zooming-in until you have 1 group and then zoom out/in.
- You can notice that the groups overlaps.

<img width="701" alt="Screenshot 2019-08-30 at 20 13 39" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8843101/64042689-bd9e1c00-cb62-11e9-98c9-c08d89da63d0.png">


Regards

