You may need to add coordinates. For example,
```
    markLine: {
                data: [[{
                    id: '1',
                    label: {
                        formatter: '1111111'
                    },
                    xAxis: -30,
                    yAxis: 30
                },
                {
                    xAxis: 50,
                    yAxis: 50
                }]]
            }
```

It seems to be a bug! I found the error may be [here](https://github.com/apache/incubator-echarts/blob/master/src/component/marker/MarkLineView.js#L368). Because the behavior returned to normal when I used the following wayÔºö
```
let temp = optData;
if (coordSys) {
    optData = zrUtil.filter(
        optData, zrUtil.curry(markLineFilter, coordSys)
    );
}
optData = temp;
```

